   Krauskopf, N. G. Broderick, R. Braive, G. Beaudoin, I. Sagnes, S.
   Barbay, Opt. Lett. 43, 3013 (2018)
   - Spike latency and response properties of an excitable micropillar
   laser F. Selmi, R. Braive, G.
   Beaudoin, I. Sagnes, R. Kuszelewicz, T. Erneux, S. Barbay, Phys. Rev. E
   94, 042219 (2016)
